#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.corrwith.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.corrwith"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corrwith:1 of
msgid "Compute pairwise correlation."
msgstr "计算成对相关性。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corrwith:3 of
msgid ""
"Pairwise correlation is computed between rows or columns of DataFrame "
"with rows or columns of Series or DataFrame. DataFrames are first aligned"
" along both axes before computing the correlations."
msgstr ""
"在 DataFrame 的行或列与 Series 或 DataFrame 的行或列之间计算成对相关性。"
"在计算相关性之前，首先沿两个轴对齐 DataFrames。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.corrwith.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corrwith:8 of
msgid "Object with which to compute correlations."
msgstr "用于计算相关性的对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corrwith:10 of
msgid ""
"The axis to use. 0 or 'index' to compute column-wise, 1 or 'columns' for "
"row-wise."
msgstr "使用的轴。0 或 'index' 表示按列计算，1 或 'columns' 表示按行计算。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corrwith:13 of
msgid "Drop missing indices from result."
msgstr "从结果中删除缺失的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corrwith:15 of
msgid ""
"Method of correlation:  * pearson : standard correlation coefficient * "
"kendall : Kendall Tau correlation coefficient * spearman : Spearman rank "
"correlation * callable: callable with input two 1d ndarrays     and "
"returning a float.  .. note::     kendall, spearman and callables not "
"supported on multiple chunks yet."
msgstr ""
"相关方法：  * pearson : 标准相关系数 * kendall : Kendall Tau 相关系数 * "
"spearman : Spearman 秩相关 * callable: 可调用对象，输入为两个一维数组，"
"返回一个浮点数。  .. note::     kendall、spearman 和可调用对象尚未支持"
"多个块。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corrwith:15 of
msgid "Method of correlation:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corrwith:17 of
msgid "pearson : standard correlation coefficient"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corrwith:18 of
msgid "kendall : Kendall Tau correlation coefficient"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corrwith:19 of
msgid "spearman : Spearman rank correlation"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corrwith:20 of
msgid "callable: callable with input two 1d ndarrays"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corrwith:21 of
msgid "and returning a float."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.corr.df_corrwith:24 of
msgid "kendall, spearman and callables not supported on multiple chunks yet."
msgstr ""

